Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.45,0:00:45.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ame agari no sora wo aogu tabi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.45,0:00:45.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I look up to \Nthe sky after the rain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:51.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nakimushi datta koro no boku wo omou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:51.15,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I think back to when I was a crybaby
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:58.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dareka no senaka wo gamushara ni oikaketa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:58.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chasing somebody's back blindly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:01.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"tsuyoku naritai" tte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:01.70,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking "I want to be stronger"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:07.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ima wa kaze ni kieta "arigatou"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:07.21,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The word "thank you" has \Nfaded into the wind now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:12.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku wa tsuyoku nareteiru no kana?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:12.38,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I getting stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:18.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kotae wa mada desou ni nai kara sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:18.05,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the answer yet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:23.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yappari mada aruiteiku yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:23.39,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll keep walking ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:25.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:25.81,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:29.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:29.11,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:34.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:34.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:39.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:39.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:45.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:45.41,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku no naka ni nagareru koe wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.84,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The voice inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:56.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,zutto zutto boku wo sasaeteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:56.01,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,keeps sustaining me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:02:01.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,itazura na ame ga jama suru kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:02:01.26,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked rain will get in my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:06.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nigedasanai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:06.10,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't walk away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.98,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:20.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:20.16,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:25.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:25.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:31.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:31.38,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:39.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinjita sono saki e to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:39.68,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,To the future I believe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the War of the Best against the Navy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy reached the Maiden Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.56,0:03:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...only to became depressed by \Nhis own feelings of weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.06,0:03:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it that you still have?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.51,0:03:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Reunited with Dark King Rayleigh! \NDecision Time for Luffy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:06.68,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,CALM BELT
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:13.52,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE BAY AT THE CLIFF COAST \NOF THE MAIDEN ISLAND
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He stopped screaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.35,0:04:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, I \Nwonder where Straw Hat is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna die if his wound opens up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.42,0:04:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.93,0:04:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I just saw a fish...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's big!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! That's a huge Sea King!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.93,0:04:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.86,0:05:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dead! It got killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--But it's huge!\N--I couldn't see what did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.64,0:05:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's scary around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A man?\N--Hey! Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.06,0:05:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.09,0:05:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Dark King Rayleigh!!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you guys. We met \Nat Sabaody Archipelago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was the first mate of Roger, \Nthe King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my ship sank in the storm \Nand I had no choice but to swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:06:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Storm?! The Calm Belt is always \Ncalm - it's never rough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There shouldn't be a storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.78,0:06:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means his ship wrecked further \Naway and he swam all the way here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a good breaststroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, that Sea King was fighting with...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only a legendary pirate could do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you sorry for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume Luffy-kun must \Nbe here on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:40.40,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:44.46,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE CENTER OF THE ISLAND: \NTHE FEMALE-ONLY EMPIRE AMAZON LILY
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:42.04,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,that Snake Princess-sama and the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...have just gone to deliver food to Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna stretch his body again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said they'll invite him \Nover when he gets better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect to see him again this soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:06:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men are interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could become a man, my body \Nwould be stretchable like his!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, maybe I'll make \Nclothes for him again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...without frills!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're separated although we're newlyweds!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like a tragic heroine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"But Hancock... No, my dear wife!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Y-Yes!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"No matter how far away from each \Nother we are, our love is forever!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.48,0:07:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Luffy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.84,0:07:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my sweet husband! My heart is aflame!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said before, Snake Princess,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.48,0:07:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just because someone hugs \Nyou and uses your name,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it doesn't mean you are married.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what counts as marriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm... That's a difficult question.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.36,0:08:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go to Sabaody now with that wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.97,0:08:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wanna see my friends \Nas soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.56,0:08:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to be there just like I promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? The submarine is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.98,0:08:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Luffy-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! The old guy Rayleigh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.21,0:08:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to see you this soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.39,0:08:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was about to head to Sabaody \Nusing the Vivre Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see my friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't think they made it there yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave my Vivre Card to Shakky...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in order to go anywhere I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark King Rayleigh! Is it really \Nyou? I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:08:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be the former Warlord...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's Jimbei, he saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I didn't expect to \Nsee a living legend here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Isn't this hat important to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't feel right without it after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen a group of pirates here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're talking about \NTrafalgar Law, he just left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.45,0:09:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that you have to rest \Nin bed for 2 more weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He saved your life, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.72,0:09:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste! We got that far...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to get in the female-only empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.56,0:09:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were allowing bears in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.09,0:09:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:10:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what the Dark King is up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever it is I'm sure that "D." will \Ncause quite a storm once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't wait to see him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.28,0:10:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Rayleigh?! You must be Rayleigh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Gloriosa! It's been awhile!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Rayleigh!\N--Ray-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you two are here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Big Sis! How could you ignore \Nthe man who saved your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the old man Rayleigh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes!\N--It's a long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, so you're awake now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't \Nslept for days worrying about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be hungry. I brought some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.41,0:10:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So go ahead and dig in...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even look at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you call it marriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Serve him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Serve him a meal already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.11,0:11:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei! These are not for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have just a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay. Luffy-kun, why don't we just eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-kun, you have to eat. Eating is living!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! That's my Luffy-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei! I said "just a little bit"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:11:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for bringing me \Nthe letter from Shakky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like she hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she's just the way she was \Nwhen you were living in Sabaody.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These girls have become very beautiful \Nand strong over the past 13 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rayleigh, Shakky, Granny Nyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You three protected us when we were \Nrunning from the Celestial Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.52,0:12:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should be providing shelter \Nfor Luffy from the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though Rayleigh \Nknows Luffy from before,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if it's easy enough for someone \Nto guess that Luffy's here,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.31,0:12:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we should be worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! What an old familiar face!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.96,0:12:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Rayleigh, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just noticed?! \NHow mad are you about him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't think the Navy \Ncan guess that he's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:13:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, the one who sent him away
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,told me that he sent him in this direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.62,0:13:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I work for the Revolutionaries army.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.30,0:13:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I have a connection with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna let them get away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.33,0:13:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And where's Monkey-chan now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about my abrupt manner earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I talk to you for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...much time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat should be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the direction that Bartholomew \NKuma blew Luffy-kun away,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is the Maiden Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found out some interesting \Ninformation about the War of the Best.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.31,0:14:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's with regards to the prison break at \NImpel Down by Luffy-kun and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.19,0:14:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I thought about how Luffy-kun was \Nable to infiltrate the great prison,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it dawned on me that Luffy-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,must have stowed away on a \NNavy ship with Hancock, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Hancock hates both \Nthe Government and men,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that she'd \Nget on a Government ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.40,0:14:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,especially not to help a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, this part is all theoretical.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.96,0:14:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say that Hancock fell in \Nlove with Monkey-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everything makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey-chan is a good-looking guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if I were Hancock,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd give him refuge on the Maiden \NIsland to spite the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:15:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a very subjective theory, Shakky.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Women's intuition is unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's my Shakky!\N--She couldn't be any more right, as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? You like it? Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy won't take action based \Non a ridiculous theory like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this place is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's get down to business.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.76,0:15:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you're gonna head \Nfor Sabaody, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to see my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you really want?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.36,0:16:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabaody Archipelago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.68,0:16:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember what happened to \Nyou guys on that island?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone focus on escaping!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As we are now, we can't beat these guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.95,0:16:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't save even one of my friends...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.72,0:17:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can face those \Ntremendous powers as you are now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.87,0:17:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to be reunited with your \Nfriends just to endure the same fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a suggestion for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it's up to you to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.76,0:17:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...do it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.50,0:18:05.68,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, on the Bowin \NIslands in the Grand Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:05.68,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,GRAND LINE - BOWIN ISLANDS
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Usopp'n!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop me, Heracles'n!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.43,0:18:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...shaking his body which has grown huge
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.52,0:18:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from eating an abundant variety \Nof food in the forest...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.44,0:18:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and running.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.76,0:18:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible'n!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not! That's why I'll try again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.59,0:18:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure Kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no'n! Usopp'n!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.08,0:19:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Usopp'n?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that. If you try \Nto get off of this island,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,terrifying living things \Nwill stand in your way
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and push you back to the forest'n.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.94,0:19:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing will stop you from \Nentering the island'n
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but once you've set foot on it, you're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one ever leaves this island alive'n!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.89,0:19:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my name is Heracles'n!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?! Usopp'n! Where did you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he's in danger'n!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea creature has just \Ncome onto the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp'n is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.08,0:20:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sweet scent from Bowin Islands \Ndraws the attention of...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.70,0:20:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...giant insects and giant birds...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and even sea creatures and Sea Kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a sea hippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't get fascinated by it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The scents lure them \Ndeeper into the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.11,0:20:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...where they find the \Nforest filled with food.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.27,0:20:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy to enter the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's hard to leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta my way! Sure Kill - Exploding Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.19,0:20:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.51,0:20:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.52,0:20:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Sabaody!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.11,0:20:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exploding Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exploding Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.58,0:21:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exploding Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exploding Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exploding Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.56,0:21:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp'n!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The islands are gonna move again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.56,0:21:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp'n! Hang onto a tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's happening again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna eat something!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.57,0:21:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name of this flower that \Nlooks like an island is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.76,0:21:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People call them the Bowin Islands
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.55,0:21:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the scientific name is Stomach \NBaron: a meat-eating plant!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.05,0:22:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp'n!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.34,0:22:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter with you, Usopp'n?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.92,0:22:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You changed since reading the \Nnewspaper that News Coo brought!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.77,0:22:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.78,0:22:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...have no time to waste here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.97,0:22:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy lost his brother in the war!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.17,0:22:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be having a very hard time now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.19,0:23:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When your friend is having a hard time,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.07,0:23:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you should be there for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.26,0:23:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.48,0:23:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy's friends take \Naction, concerned for him,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.27,0:23:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Nami is held captive by \Nthe researchers of Weatheria.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.29,0:23:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, on Winter Island, Franky heads to \Na certain place in search of an ice-breaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.60,0:23:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What extremely dangerous \Nbutton has he found there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.81,0:23:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Back to Our Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.49,0:23:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Jail Break at the Sky Island and \Nthe Incident on the Winter Island!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.02,0:23:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
